This paper deals with the problem of learning item-clusters under local differential privacy, which is a topic related to machine learning and data privacy. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.DB (Databases).
